FBIS3-36009 "drsov022_f_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-022 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Feb 1994 National Affairs Self-Defense Detachments `on Full Combat Alert' LD0102130394 Kiev UNIAR in Ukrainian 1218 GMT 1 Feb 94 LD0102130394 Kiev UNIAR Language: Ukrainian Article Type:BFN [Text] Kiev, 1 Feb -- As Vasyl Bilous, press adviser of the Ukrainian National Assembly has stated, Yuriy Meshkov's victory in the Crimean presidential elections will lead to a civil war. In his words, detachments of the UNA-UNSO [Ukrainian National Assembly-Ukrainian National Self-Defense] are at present on full combat alert: "We are prepared to react to all events in the Crimea."
